            <title>[LU-17023] lsvcgssd can use a realm different from default realm</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17023</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lsvcgssd uses the default_realm and try to match principals only exactly matching this realm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We would like to be able to specify a different realm than the default one, ie:&lt;br/&gt;
lsvcgss -R &amp;lt;DOMAIN.COM&amp;gt; -k -m -o -v&lt;/p&gt;</description>
